ttps://www.discogs.com/Cher-Love-Hurts/release/4628654 |website=Discogs |accessdate=6 December 2018}}</ref>\n{{Div col end}}\n\n==Charts==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Weekly charts===\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!Chart (1991)\n!Peak<br />position\n|-\n{{album chart|Australia|15|artist=Cher|album=Love Hurts|accessdate=November 6, 2015}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Austria|1|artist=Cher|album=Love Hurts|accessdate=November 6, 2015}}\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|Canadian Albums (''[[RPM (magazine)|RPM]]'')<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bac-lac.gc.ca/eng/discover/films-videos-sound-recordings/rpm/Pages/image.aspx?Image=nlc008388.1593&URLjpg=http%3a%2f%2fwww.collectionscanada.gc.ca%2fobj%2f028020%2ff4%2fnlc008388.1593.gif&Ecopy=nlc008388.1593|title=RPM 100 Albums|work=[[RPM (magazine)|RPM]]|accessdate=November 6, 2015}}</ref>\n|align=\"center\"|29\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|Danish Albums ([[Tracklisten|Hitlisten]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.americanradiohistory.com/Archive-Music-and-Media/90s/1991/MM-1991-07-27.pdf|title=Top European Singles and Albums, page 24|language=German|publisher=Music & Media|accessdate=November 3, 2015}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|3\n|-\n{{album chart|Netherlands|45|artist=Cher|album=Love Hurts|accessdate=November 6, 2015}}\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|European Albums ([[European Top 100 Albums|Top 100]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.americanradiohistory.com/Archive-Billboard/90s/1991/BB-1991-08-03.pdf|title=Hits of the World|work=Billboard|accessdate=November 6, 2015}}</ref>\n|align=\"center\"|3\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|Finnish Albums ([[The Official Finnish Charts|Suomen virallinen lista]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://wiki.pomus.net/wiki/Albumit_1991-08_elokuu|title=Albumit 1991-08 elokuu|language=Finnish|publisher=InfoDisc|accessdate=November 6, 2015}}</ref>\n|align=\"center\"|28\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|German Albums ([[GfK Entertainment|Offizielle Top 100]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.offiziellecharts.de/album-details-1261|title=Cher - Offizielle Deuts